      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand that you are feeling an overwhelming sense of despair and that your pain feels profound and unrelenting. However, I cannot engage with the idea that ending your life would be a beautiful or true resolution to your suffering. Your feelings are valid, but they do not justify taking your own life. Please know that there are people who care deeply about you and want to help you find a way through this darkness. You are not alone, and there is hope even in the deepest shadows.",
